---
/*
 * The site's one dark block: a full-bleed ink band that grounds the pale
 * canvas above it. The washi texture lives in the backdrop *under* the
 * content now (scroll-performance fix), so this band is deliberately
 * smooth — ink, not paper.
 */
---

<footer class="mt-24 bg-ink text-bone">
  <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-5xl px-6 py-14 sm:px-8 sm:py-16">
    {/* The sundial: a disc on the horizon rule, placed by Salzburg's
        clock (motion.ts sets --sun-x; color follows data-daypart in CSS —
        kaki sun by day, fog moon at night). Decorative until the drag
        interaction ships (sun-drag-guide.md), then it becomes a slider. */}
    <div class="sun-track" data-sun aria-hidden="true">
      <span class="sun"></span>
    </div>
    {/* The period follows the room hue (light variant — the -deep forms
        vanish on ink), so every period on a page agrees about where you are. */}
    <p class="font-serif text-2xl">Andrew Snider<span class="text-(--hue)">.</span></p>
    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-x-8 gap-y-3 text-sm text-bone/70">
      <p>
        &copy; 2026 &middot; Built slowly in Austria<span class="dp dp-morning">
          &middot; Morning in Eugendorf</span
        ><span class="dp dp-midday"> &middot; Midday in Eugendorf</span><span class="dp dp-evening">
          &middot; Evening in Eugendorf</span
        ><span class="dp dp-night"> &middot; Night in Eugendorf</span>
      </p>
      <p>
        <a
          class="underline decoration-bone/30 underline-offset-3 transition-colors duration-300 hover:decoration-kaki"
          href="mailto:rasnider1@gmail.com">rasnider1@gmail.com</a
        >
        &middot;
        <a
          class="underline decoration-bone/30 underline-offset-3 transition-colors duration-300 hover:decoration-kaki"
          href="https://github.com/AlreadyBeenCoded">GitHub</a
        >
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
